cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SD

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for transforming word embeddings from one language to another. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves unsupervised learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves techniques for improving word embeddings, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques for solving the problem of missing words in a model, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another possible category. Finally, the paper involves techniques for handling data scarcity, which falls under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
